  {
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Here some extracts from our JS code @Haroenv \r\n\r\n```javascript\r\n// [...]\r\n\r\nvar facets_for_select = [{\r\n    name: 'color',\r\n    attribute_name: 'color_original',\r\n    header_text: 'Couleurs',\r\n    sort_by: ['isRefined', 'name:asc'],\r\n    search_for_facet_values: {\r\n      placeholder: 'Recherchez une couleur',\r\n      no_results: 'Aucune couleur ne correspond'\r\n    },\r\n  },{\r\n\r\n// [...]\r\n\r\n  facets_for_select.forEach(function(facet_config) {\r\n    // [...]\r\n    try {\r\n      search.addWidget(\r\n        instantsearch.widgets.refinementList({\r\n          autoHideContainer: true,\r\n          container: '#filter-' + facet_config.name,\r\n          attributeName: facet_config.attribute_name,\r\n          sortBy: facet_config.sort_by ? facet_config.sort_by : ['isRefined', 'count:desc', 'name:asc'],\r\n          limit: facet_config.limit ? facet_config.limit : 200,\r\n          operator: 'or',\r\n          cssClasses: cssClasses_for.filters,\r\n          templates: {\r\n            header: getHeader( facet_config.header_text ),\r\n            item : facet_config.getItem ? facet_config.getItem : getItem,\r\n          },\r\n          searchForFacetValues: facet_config.search_for_facet_values && {\r\n            placeholder: facet_config.search_for_facet_values.placeholder,\r\n            templates: {\r\n              noResults: '<div class=\"sffv_no-results\">' +\r\n                facet_config.search_for_facet_values.no_results +\r\n                ' pour cette catégorie.</div>'\r\n            }\r\n          }\r\n        })\r\n      );\r\n    } catch (e) {\r\n      console.debug('Could not init widgets for: ' + facet_config.name)\r\n    }\r\n  });\r\n```\r\n",
    "created_at": "2017-05-18T18:01:47Z",
